126
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:33,750
But,

127
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,290
if you stay

128
00:06:35,290 --> 00:06:36,620
and finish today's shoot,

129
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,200
