with you accusing me.

326
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:30,790
You...

327
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:35,000
You pull the trigger

328
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,290
while someone else handles the ammo.

329
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:38,700
