En and I are coming back tomorrow]

347
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:18,540
Do you like Han Chengchi that much?

348
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:19,250
Yes.

349
00:17:19,410 --> 00:17:20,540
I do.

350
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:21,540
