544
00:27:52,370 --> 00:27:53,750
Isn't this Mrs. Sheng?

545
00:27:53,950 --> 00:27:54,830
What a coincidence.

546
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:56,080
You're back too.

547
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:58,580
Why didn't Shi come with you?

548
00:27:59,950 --> 00:28:01,750
